Chip Comes To Visit
In this first session Chip is making his third of three visits. He comes in full uniform, follows me upstairs and slowly strips out of his pants, leaving on his cover (what Marines call their hat) and shirt and watches his video that he did with AJ on his previous visit. This is a shorter session than his first solo which comes last on the tape, but it's intense and very very hot. This boy shoots loads like a machine and drenches himself in his own man juice. Chip is a bit of a country boy and his personality comes off on camera very well. You'll just wanna wrap him up and keep him forever.
title: Chip
